{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/python_requirements/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Funny Eagle","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"89126fd7-3281-5f7d-810a-d743c0036aae","excerpt":"在 Python 项目中生成  文件是一个常见的需求，用于记录项目所依赖的所有包及其版本。这样可以确保在其他环境中也能正确安装相同的依赖。\n以下是一些常用的方法来生成  文件： 方法一：使用   命…","html":"<p>在 Python 项目中生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件是一个常见的需求，用于记录项目所依赖的所有包及其版本。这样可以确保在其他环境中也能正确安装相同的依赖。\n以下是一些常用的方法来生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件：</p>\n<h3 id=\"方法一使用-code-classlanguage-textpip-freezecode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-code-classlanguage-textpip-freezecode\" aria-label=\"方法一使用 code classlanguage textpip freezecode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>方法一：使用 <code class=\"language-text\">pip freeze</code></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">pip freeze</code> 命令可以列出当前环境中所有已安装的包及其版本。你可以将这些信息重定向到 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件中。</p>\n<h4 id=\"步骤\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" aria-label=\"步骤 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>步骤</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>激活你的虚拟环境</strong>（如果使用了虚拟环境）：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> venv/bin/activate  <span class=\"token comment\"># Linux/MacOS</span>\n.<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>venv<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Scripts<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>activate  <span class=\"token comment\"># Windows</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">pip freeze <span class=\"token operator\">></span> requirements.txt</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"方法二使用-code-classlanguage-textpipreqscode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-code-classlanguage-textpipreqscode\" aria-label=\"方法二使用 code classlanguage textpipreqscode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>方法二：使用 <code class=\"language-text\">pipreqs</code></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">pipreqs</code> 是一个第三方工具，可以根据项目中的导入语句自动生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件。这种方法可以更精确地生成项目所需的依赖，而不是列出所有已安装的包。</p>\n<h4 id=\"安装-code-classlanguage-textpipreqscode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-code-classlanguage-textpipreqscode\" aria-label=\"安装 code classlanguage textpipreqscode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装 <code class=\"language-text\">pipreqs</code></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">pip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> pipreqs</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"生成-code-classlanguage-textrequirementstxtcode-文件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-code-classlanguage-textrequirementstxtcode-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"生成 code classlanguage textrequirementstxtcode 文件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">pipreqs /path/to/your/project</code></pre></div>\n<p>例如，如果你的项目位于 <code class=\"language-text\">my_project</code> 目录下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">pipreqs my_project</code></pre></div>\n<p>这将会在 <code class=\"language-text\">my_project</code> 目录下生成一个 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件。</p>\n<h3 id=\"方法三使用-code-classlanguage-textpoetrycode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%89%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-code-classlanguage-textpoetrycode\" aria-label=\"方法三使用 code classlanguage textpoetrycode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>方法三：使用 <code class=\"language-text\">Poetry</code></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Poetry</code> 是一个现代的 Python 包管理和依赖管理工具，它可以自动生成和管理 <code class=\"language-text\">pyproject.toml</code> 和 <code class=\"language-text\">poetry.lock</code> 文件，也可以生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件。</p>\n<h4 id=\"安装-code-classlanguage-textpoetrycode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-code-classlanguage-textpoetrycode\" aria-label=\"安装 code classlanguage textpoetrycode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装 <code class=\"language-text\">Poetry</code></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-sSL</span> https://install.python-poetry.org <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> python3 -</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"初始化项目\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE\" aria-label=\"初始化项目 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>初始化项目</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> my_project\npoetry init</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"添加依赖\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96\" aria-label=\"添加依赖 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>添加依赖</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">poetry <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>package<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">poetry <span class=\"token function\">add</span> requests</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"生成-code-classlanguage-textrequirementstxtcode-文件-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-code-classlanguage-textrequirementstxtcode-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-1\" aria-label=\"生成 code classlanguage textrequirementstxtcode 文件 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">poetry <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-f</span> requirements.txt <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--output</span> requirements.txt</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"方法四使用-code-classlanguage-textpip-toolscode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%9B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-code-classlanguage-textpip-toolscode\" aria-label=\"方法四使用 code classlanguage textpip toolscode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>方法四：使用 <code class=\"language-text\">pip-tools</code></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">pip-tools</code> 是一组命令行工具，用于编译和更新 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件。</p>\n<h4 id=\"安装-code-classlanguage-textpip-toolscode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-code-classlanguage-textpip-toolscode\" aria-label=\"安装 code classlanguage textpip toolscode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装 <code class=\"language-text\">pip-tools</code></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">pip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> pip-tools</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"生成-code-classlanguage-textrequirementstxtcode-文件-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-code-classlanguage-textrequirementstxtcode-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-2\" aria-label=\"生成 code classlanguage textrequirementstxtcode 文件 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>创建 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.in</code> 文件</strong>，列出项目所需的包：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"plaintext\"><pre class=\"language-plaintext\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">requests</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt</code> 文件</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">pip-compile requirements.in</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"方法五使用-code-classlanguage-textpipenvcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%94%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-code-classlanguage-textpipenvcode\" aria-label=\"方法五使用 code classlanguage textpipenvcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>方法五：使用 <code class=\"language-text\">pipenv</code></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Pipenv</code> 是一个用于管理 Python 项目依赖的工具，它可以生成 <code class=\"language-text\">Pipfile</code> 和 <code class=\"language-text\">Pipfile.lock</code> 文件，也可以生成 <code class=\"language-text\">requirements.txt<